Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:11.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium grants us another possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.59,0:24:15.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:17.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Door to a New World.
